+ What is This?

This is the Borealis Constant Theme, created by [[*user MisterFrown]] specifically for his Borealis Constant series. Use of it outside the series is discouraged. If you would like to write something in the series, feel free to reach out!

+ How to Use

Put the following code above any page to use:

> [[include :scp-wiki:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]
> [[include :scp-wiki:theme:borealis-constant-theme]]

+++ Default SPC Variant

For those who wish to use this theme as just a general-purpose SPC theme unrelated to the series, here is a variant created specifically for that:

> [[include :scp-wiki:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]
> [[include :scp-wiki:theme:borealis-constant-theme
> @@|spc=--]@@
> ]]

As this is a Black Highlighter based theme, you are required to utilize it as well if you wish to use this one. Please consult [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/theme:black-highlighter-theme this page] for more information.

